\newlabel{tab:tpcds_time}{{4}{15}{TPC-DS workload execution time (PostgreSQL~14, Scale Factor~10, 10 drift rounds at $\approx 3\%$ each). OASIS recovers 52.0\% of Full ANALYZE's improvement over stale statistics}{table.caption.21}{}}
